il-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ae4af3f6cdf48dc9e84eea518c60de84be885be","tid":1111251,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T02:11:18.000Z","msg":"黎明詩 鄭秀文<br />\n<br />\n兩位差不多時期出道的女歌手，以起步成績計，黎明詩比鄭秀文更受注目，但以長途成績計，當然冇得比。93年黎明詩的〈敢恨敢愛〉 與鄭秀文〈衝動點唱〉/ 許志安〈唯獨是你不可取替〉改編同一首日文歌。<br />\n<br />\n鄭秀文 推出首張個人大碟年份 : 1990<br />\n新人獎 : 叱咤冇、無線冇、港台最有前途新人獎優異獎<br />\n<br />\n黎明詩 推出首張個人大碟年份 : 1991<br />\n新人獎 : 叱咤樂壇生力軍女歌手金獎、無線最受歡迎新人獎銅獎、港台最有前途新人獎銅獎"},{"pid":"f7e68da0a47f9baeefaf917fbd23a3c4ebd4e07d","tid":1111251,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T02:50:42.000Z","msg":"應該唔會再見到依兩個人合唱，就算有冇發生最近單野都好 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0dfcc2eb156b0375eb6404ad13803ad27a8b853","tid":1111251,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T04:06:12.000Z","msg":"最後一貼 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F130749_f6d79dfbdfb935b547b31d6eec79afed.png&h=0657fa5a&s={SIZE}\" />，冇人睇費事再嘥時間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四首都係改編同一首而有兩首係佢兩個<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q0ZGt1srNG8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ0ZGt1srNG8&d=cvAaz42KU7EB3jG3uroQKANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=1915be8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q0ZGt1srNG8</a><br />\n敢恨敢愛 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8ynQbjcsMz8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8ynQbjcsMz8&d=cvAaz4